## Integration Architecture

```text
CashierWorkspace
  │
  ├── TableGrid → OnTableSelected → load order
  │
  ├── OrderPanel (manages internal flow):
  │     ├── [Confirm] → POST /orders/{id}/confirm
  │     ├── [Payment] → PaymentDialog (inline)
  │     │     └── POST /payments → OnPaymentComplete
  │     ├── ReceiptPreview (inline, after payment)
  │     │     ├── [Print] → POST /receipts/customer
  │     │     ├── [Close Table] → POST /tables/{id}/release
  │     │     └── [Skip] → return to grid
  │     └── OnTableOpened → HandleTableOperationComplete()
  │         → _tableRefreshVersion++ (grid reloads)
  │         → _selectedTableId = null (panel clears)
  │
  ├── MenuModal → OnProductAdded → POST /orders/{id}/items → refresh
  │
  └── ToastNotification → success/error feedback
```

## Complete End-to-End Flow

```
1. [TableGrid] Click Available → OrderPanel shows
2. [OrderPanel] Click [Open Table] → POST /tables/{id}/open → POST /orders → Draft order
3. [OrderPanel] Click [+ Add Item] → MenuModal opens
4. [MenuModal] Click product → POST /orders/{id}/items → toast → stays open
5. [OrderPanel] Click [✓ Confirm Order] → POST /orders/{id}/confirm → Confirmed
6. [OrderPanel] Click [Pay Now] → PaymentDialog
7. [PaymentDialog] Select method, enter amount, Pay → POST /payments → ReceiptPreview
8. [ReceiptPreview] Click [Print & Close Table] → POST /receipts + POST /tables/{id}/release
9. [TableGrid] Table shows Available, OrderPanel clears
```

## API Sequence

| Step | Action | Endpoint | Component |
|------|--------|----------|-----------|
| 1 | Open table | `POST /tables/{id}/open` | OrderPanel |
| 2 | Create order | `POST /orders` | OrderPanel |
| 3 | Add item | `POST /orders/{id}/items` | CashierWorkspace |
| 4 | Confirm | `POST /orders/{id}/confirm` | OrderPanel |
| 5 | Payment | `POST /payments` | PaymentDialog |
| 6 | Print receipt | `POST /receipts/customer` | ReceiptPreview |
| 7 | Release table | `POST /tables/{id}/release` | ReceiptPreview |
| 8 | Refresh grid | `GET /tables` | TableGrid |

